<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>Re: Racewar sever will be dumb</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?Ice">Ice</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 7:43 a.m. 5/6/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Re: Racewar sever will be dumb<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/pvp.cgi?read=2137" TARGET=_self>Racewar sever will be dumb</A> (Ghouldan)
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>I dont know about many of you but i really thought faction hits on killing your own race was something that was supposed to be on Rallos Zek anyway. When you are a newbie, or even 1-13 i would say race wars are fun, and raids are common. But as your character gets older you find many of your on race grouping with other races, and when you get even bigger in levels, you see huge amounts of multi racial people together.,, From a roleplaying aspect Dark elfs, Trolls, and Ogres are supposed to be hated by most races, but yet they still hang with other races,. I mean when people are at Cazic and Basher Hard walks up and bashes some High elf in your group it is for a reason, the reason being because they supposed to be not welcome there,. Now i find it to common to go up and attack and opposing race, only to have your own race attack you back because they were grouped with them. I dont know but i think if they just make a race war server, and leave relloz zek the way it is, it will become more or less like the abyss shard on uo, were everyones hacking each other rather than the good old days people remembered in uo when it was good vs. evil..

<BR>
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
